{"tid":390351,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Fifa 18 Switch版 有無標價?","createTime":"2017-09-07T04:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T06:12:52.000Z","uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"260c014ef2f3e076b97f753a70f848a8d1bdac40","tid":390351,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"暫時淨係見到得其他平台有價錢 <br />\n但好似唔見Switch有<br />\n<br />\n《FIFA 18》將推出三個版本：標準版、Ronaldo 版，以及超級球星版（標誌版），遊戲目前已於各個平台接受預訂。售價分別為59.99美元（約470港元）、79.99美元（約620港元）及、99.99美元（約780港元）。暫時見香港地區 PlayStation Store 、 Microsoft Store 及 Origin 預購標誌版均700有找，比美金抵玩。預購 Ronaldo 版及超級球星版（標誌版）的玩家更可提早3天開始進行遊戲。"},{"pid":"6263dbbb4ff013582ab2e75367382c67b9cba34e","tid":390351,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"有冇demo"},{"pid":"bb18f90f49ff319965f70ecd0871e97ae0bc1892","tid":390351,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇demo</blockquote><br />\n無 demo得PS4 XBOX同PC"},{"pid":"943d1e6408ba851c9ec8eb7369b8772cd0443364","tid":390351,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"應該都係over$400架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ccfc3c2439da77ed06aaf3dfedd852cfa8f7ce","tid":390351,"uid":1755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/135805_e98afb3aeba1d7e0f62283e09af959f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F135805_e98afb3aeba1d7e0f62283e09af959f4.jpg&h=78cb1aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早幾日响日本見到"},{"pid":"bc8ea0ebd6f5db03adcf5c68a79858742a11ae86","tid":390351,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/135805_e98a